name: Ladybug Christmas Ornament
description:
Made to order:

Red Ladybug Christmas Tree Ornament.

This sweet little ladybug will look quite festive and at home on your tree this year!

Hand Sculpted from polymer clay the ornament is painted and given a light coat of a water based sealer. Each ladybug measures approximately 2 inches by 2 inches. Your item will arrive ready to hang on a coordinating jute cord within a muslin drawstring bag for storage.

I use no molds in the making of my ornaments. As such no two will look exactly the same, each ladybug will have its own unique coloring and shape. Pictures are representative of what your ornament will look like. Please allow for seven business days for Made to Order items to be created prior to shipping.
